001package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog;
002
003import org.apache.commons.lang3.Validate;
004import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.annotations.HistoryLogProps;
005import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Bytes;
006import com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.helpers.Dates;
007
008import java.time.Instant;
009
010@HistoryLogProps(
011    opCode = 14,
012    displayName = "Date Change",
013    internalName = "LID_DATE_CHANGED",
014    usedByAndroid = true,
015    usedByTidepool = true
016)
017public class DateChangeHistoryLog extends HistoryLog {
018    
019    private long datePrior;
020    private long dateAfter;
021    private long rawRTCTime;
022    
023    public DateChangeHistoryLog() {}
024    
025    public DateChangeHistoryLog(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long datePrior, long dateAfter, long rawRTCTime) {
026        this.cargo = buildCargo(pumpTimeSec, sequenceNum, datePrior, dateAfter, rawRTCTime);
027        this.pumpTimeSec = pumpTimeSec;
028        this.sequenceNum = sequenceNum;
029        this.datePrior = datePrior;
030        this.dateAfter = dateAfter;
031        this.rawRTCTime = rawRTCTime;
032        
033    }
034
035    public int typeId() {
036        return 14;
037    }
038
039    /**
040     * <table border="1">
041     * <caption>Parsed fields for DateChangeHistoryLog:</caption>
042     * <tr><td><code>datePrior</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10)</code></td></tr>
043     * <tr><td><code>dateAfter</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14)</code></td></tr>
044     * <tr><td><code>rawRTCTime</code></td><td><code>Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18)</code></td></tr>
045     * </table>
046     */
047    public void parse(byte[] raw) {
048        Validate.isTrue(raw.length == 26);
049        this.cargo = raw;
050        parseBase(raw);
051        this.datePrior = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 10);
052        this.dateAfter = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 14);
053        this.rawRTCTime = Bytes.readUint32(raw, 18);
054        
055    }
056
057    
058    /**
059     * <table border="1">
060     * <caption>Byte layout for DateChangeHistoryLog.buildCargo(...):</caption>
061     * <tr><th>Offset</th><th>Description</th></tr>
062     * <tr><td>0</td><td><code>new byte[]{14} [element 0]</code></td></tr>
063     * <tr><td>1</td><td><code>new byte[]{0} [element 1]</code></td></tr>
064     * <tr><td>2</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
065     * <tr><td>3</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
066     * <tr><td>4</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
067     * <tr><td>5</td><td><code>toUint32(pumpTimeSec) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
068     * <tr><td>6</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
069     * <tr><td>7</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
070     * <tr><td>8</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
071     * <tr><td>9</td><td><code>toUint32(sequenceNum) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
072     * <tr><td>10</td><td><code>toUint32(datePrior) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
073     * <tr><td>11</td><td><code>toUint32(datePrior) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
074     * <tr><td>12</td><td><code>toUint32(datePrior) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
075     * <tr><td>13</td><td><code>toUint32(datePrior) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
076     * <tr><td>14</td><td><code>toUint32(dateAfter) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
077     * <tr><td>15</td><td><code>toUint32(dateAfter) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
078     * <tr><td>16</td><td><code>toUint32(dateAfter) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
079     * <tr><td>17</td><td><code>toUint32(dateAfter) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
080     * <tr><td>18</td><td><code>toUint32(rawRTCTime) [byte 0]</code></td></tr>
081     * <tr><td>19</td><td><code>toUint32(rawRTCTime) [byte 1]</code></td></tr>
082     * <tr><td>20</td><td><code>toUint32(rawRTCTime) [byte 2]</code></td></tr>
083     * <tr><td>21</td><td><code>toUint32(rawRTCTime) [byte 3]</code></td></tr>
084     * </table>
085     */
086    public static byte[] buildCargo(long pumpTimeSec, long sequenceNum, long datePrior, long dateAfter, long rawRTCTime) {
087        return Bytes.combine(
088            new byte[]{14, 0},
089            Bytes.toUint32(pumpTimeSec),
090            Bytes.toUint32(sequenceNum),
091            Bytes.toUint32(datePrior), 
092            Bytes.toUint32(dateAfter), 
093            Bytes.toUint32(rawRTCTime),
094            new byte[4]);
095    }
096    
097    public long getDatePrior() {
098        return datePrior;
099    }
100    public long getDateAfter() {
101        return dateAfter;
102    }
103    public long getRawRTCTime() {
104        return rawRTCTime;
105    }
106
107    public Instant getDatePriorInstant() {
108        return Dates.fromJan12008EpochDaysToDate(datePrior);
109    }
110
111    public Instant getDateAfterInstant() {
112        return Dates.fromJan12008EpochDaysToDate(dateAfter);
113    }
114}
